    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle arrives in true showroom condition, having been maintained to the highest possible standards since its inception. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a life of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. With a complete, documented service history and zero compromises in performance or aesthetics, this is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
